data.text:
Flip it~

How do you feel about Him?…
*That*’s actual, because that’s coming from *you*-

Anything else
is a voice coming from outside you..
💓🐍🗯

When you release faith in that,
grace has an amazing way of making that your reality-
Effortlessly~💓💞💗

https://t.co/rPr7DpQWcA

Way, *waaay* too highly-
Lies of ''brokenness~''💔

Live from an Actual expression
that overflows The Life inside you..💓💗
🐳
💙

https://t.co/Gz4kqXUbxK
